<lyrics>[V1]
 1- mʿ rby yswʿ ʿly̱ ṭwl ạlkẖṭ hạmsẖy zy mạ byqwl bạlḍbṭ
 hạmsẖy frḥạn wyạh ʿly̱ ṭwl dạ ạnạ qlby bḥbh byh msẖgẖwl
 ạlqrạr- wtmly fy ʿyd mʿ rby sʿyd
 2- mʿ rby yswʿ wlạ fysẖ ạḥzạn btạ̉tẖr fy wmsẖ zʿlạn
 mhmạ yḥạwl yḥạrbny ạlsẖyṭạn mʿ rby yswʿ ykẖrj kẖsrạn
 3- mʿ rby yswʿ ạ̉frạḥy tzyd fy ạllyl fy ạlṣbḥ tmly sʿyd
 wlsạny yrtl bạlthlyl wlạ ʿmrh fy mrẗ ạlfrḥ qlyl</lyrics>
<title>mʿ rby yswʿ</title>
</song>